descriptionHtml:
This mod adds 24 new books to Skyrim.   The books can be found in a chest in the College of Winterhold behind the librarian\'s desk.  You can also find them randomly in dungeons.

Book List
------------
-Apple Farm
-Dog Princess
-Dovahkiin\'s Prayer
-Gone But Not Forgotten
-Legacy of the Dovahkiin
-Purple Hash Browns & Ice Cream Sandwiches
-Siddgeir\'s Christmas
-Sheogorath\'s Crazy Rambling Volumes 1-10
-Sheogorath\'s Adventure
-The Eternal Fight
-The Legend of Rainbow Bridge
-The New Year\'s Party
-The New Vet
-Ulfric\'s Birthday
-Ulfric\'s Christmas

Don\'t be surprised if the Sheogorath books don\'t make much sense. They were written by him so they are supposed to be crazy.
author: RoxyBear
